{"tid":2063532,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「有國才有家」係中國洗腦教腦嘅第一步","createTime":"2020-06-14T05:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T13:33:09.000Z","uid":47496,"like":57,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2498e93841dfd020e30e916497ed1fde4d03b2","tid":2063532,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Evmy2MOKR4o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEvmy2MOKR4o&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=cb9fd49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Evmy2MOKR4o</a><br />\n<br />\n宣傳片都出埋<br />\n而家啲中國人都係受呢套思想所控制<br />\n希望大家要清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港正步向中國洗腦式教育去控制思想<br />\n「國家」一詞被官方定義為「有國後有家」<br />\n但《大學》八目由「明明德」嘅格物、致知、誠意、正心及修身做起，之後才發揮到「親民」嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">齊家</span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">治國</span></span>及<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平天下</span></span>，以達到「止於至善」嘅境界<br />\n當年嘅儒家思想被扭曲成咁我真係好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家要將「國」同「黨」綑綁埋一齊<br />\n總之，一室之不治，何以天下國家為？"},{"pid":"89a1491fd7504d987693058aee5efeb707d7a72a","tid":2063532,"uid":76603,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"有國才有家 香港要獨立"},{"pid":"aa95befecdabc0c931155d90974da9c28ebc99ec","tid":2063532,"uid":95344,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"北韓是個國，但入面有既家又如何？"},{"pid":"4112a67d7585bd00c8a83eb35a0e44da2917093c","tid":2063532,"uid":55835,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老母呀<br />\n<br />\n有家才有國 ok? <br />\n<br />\n古人撚係有國概念先呀？<br />\n<br />\n從來都係<br />\n有人才有家<br />\n有家才有國</span>"},{"pid":"8ed926905342f31cb1be040fa48ec195ca23ebe6","tid":2063532,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:57:14.000Z","msg":"有家不用有國"},{"pid":"ed49a45a24620c70afa60dbe4bcb48a20eb4d1af","tid":2063532,"uid":286038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"中共=家和國，明白了?!"},{"pid":"a2167f622e359709a846fad303208ee7254074e0","tid":2063532,"uid":47496,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ed49a45a24620c70afa60dbe4bcb48a20eb4d1af","tid":2063532,"uid":286038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"中共=家和國，明白了?!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:12:59.000Z","msg":"中共=所有家屬於國"},{"pid":"d301c92713fe1cbaa78df4ad1d7d1976fd741eac","tid":2063532,"uid":61396,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"無人邊有家<br />\n無家邊有國<br />\n<br />\n國佢老母"},{"pid":"9569149cd1c5ee5deddd6067b8fe9b1d80e745f4","tid":2063532,"uid":42435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"香港獨立才有自己的家"},{"pid":"53482c5549ffe699af2acb8fae311ad89e848b14","tid":2063532,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"理撚得佢家先定國先<br />\n總之比中共統治就一定係無民主無人權無自由"},{"pid":"d6f91f8f597b3616ca625a23e79099030564f4ff","tid":2063532,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"家同國唔係雞同雞蛋既概念<br />\n<br />\n如果國係政權, 家係人組成<br />\n如果有國才有家係成立<br />\n即係話呢個世界要先有政權,再有家/人<br />\n係人都知政權係生唔到人出黎<br />\n一定係有人,再有家,再有部落,再有社會,最後先有政權<br />\n<br />\n如果國係國家版圖<br />\n有地方先有家係部份成立<br />\n有地有人先有家,但政權唔係必須<br />\n所以就算愛國我都係愛中國呢個土地<br />\n關你共產政權乜撚野事?"},{"pid":"c8e16e7440b08ec9f211d008aa46c747f97833dc","tid":2063532,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4112a67d7585bd00c8a83eb35a0e44da2917093c","tid":2063532,"uid":55835,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:54:04.000Z","msg":"<span sty